          Economic Integration
        </h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <div
